  <brief_title>Cold Snare Polypectomy Vs. Cold Forceps Polypectomy Using Narrow-band Imaging Endoscopy for Removal of Diminutive Colorectal Polyps</brief_title>
  <official_title>Prospective Comparison of Cold Snare Polypectomy and Cold Forceps Polypectomy Using Narrow-band Imaging Endoscopy for Diminutive Colorectal Polyps</official_title>
  <sponsors>
